Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
if iBenchStyle = 1 then _seatBearingHeight = seatHeight - 0.045 endif
if iBenchStyle = 2 then _seatBearingHeight = seatHeight - 0.025 endif
if iBenchStyle = 3 then _seatBearingHeight = 0.503 / 0.3999 * (seatHeight - ZZYZX * 0.1031 / 0.503) endif
Symbol.Script_VL:
!Hide all parameters from UI hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`
if gs_cont_pen<=0 or gs_cont_pen>=255 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if gs_fill_pen<=0 or gs_fill_pen>=255 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91
values "iBenchStyle" 1, 2, 3, 4
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iBenchStyle" then if iBenchStyle = 4 then ZZYZX = seatHeight lock "gs_frame_mat" else ZZYZX = seatHeight + backrestHeight if iBenchStyle = 1 then lock "gs_frame_mat" else lock "gs_stand_mat" endif endif parameters ZZYZX = ZZYZX endif
values "ZZYZX" range [0.15,)
if iBenchStyle = 4 then lock "seatHeight" if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "ZZYZX" then seatHeight = ZZYZX parameters seatHeight = seatHeight endif else if iBenchStyle = 1 or iBenchStyle = 2 then values "seatHeight" range [0.1, ZZYZX - 0.05] endif
if iBenchStyle = 3 then values "seatHeight" range [ZZYZX * 0.20497 + 0.01, ZZYZX - 0.05] endif
backrestHeight = ZZYZX - seatHeight parameters backrestHeight = backrestHeight endif
Symbol.Script_UI:

pageStartY = 0 pageStartX = 0
! ============================================================================= ! Display actual tabpages ! ============================================================================= ui_dialog `Параметры Скамьи` ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
ui_page TABID_StylePage, TABID_Root, `Стиль и Размеры`, "uiTab_Dimension_flat(1)" gosub "StyleAndDimensionsPage"
ui_page TABID_RepresentationAndSurfaces, TABID_Root, `Отображение и Покрытия`, "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" gosub "RepresentationAndSurfacesPage"

! ============================================================================== !Subroutines ! ==============================================================================
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "StyleAndDimensionsPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
pageStartY = 5 _infHeight = 19 _outfHeight = 15 _yOffset = 4 x1 = 0 x2 = 123 x3 = 231 x4 = 354 dy = 24
_yCurr = pageStartY
ui_outfield `Высота Сидения`, x1, _yCurr, x2 - 3, _outfHeight ui_infield "seatHeight", x2, _yCurr-_yOffset, 90, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Высота Сидения`
_yCurr = _yCurr + dy
ui_infield{4} "iBenchStyle", 0, 24, 444, 241, 1, 1, !"OutdoorBench_Style.png" 4, 1, 105, 125, 90, 90, 1, "", 4, 2, "", 1, 3, "", 2, 4, "", 3 ui_tooltip `Стиль Скамьи`
return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "RepresentationAndSurfacesPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
_idx = 1 dim paramNameReprArray[] dim childFlagReprArray[] dim iconNameReprArray[]
paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_2D_representation" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 0 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = ""
_idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_cont_pen" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 1 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = "ui_list_contourPen_flat(1)"
_idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_fill_type" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 1 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = "ui_list_fillType_flat(1)"
_idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_fill_pen" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 1 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = "ui_list_fillPen_flat(1)"
_idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_back_pen" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 1 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = "ui_list_fillBgPen_flat(1)"
_idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_3D_representation" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 0 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = ""
_idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_detlevel_3D_m" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 1 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = "ui_list_detailLevel3D_flat(1)"
if gs_detlevel_3D_m <> DLEV3D_OFF then _idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_shadow" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 1 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = "ui_list_shadow_flat(1)" endif
_idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_material" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 0 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = ""
_idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_seat_mat" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 1 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = "ui_list_surface_flat(1)"
if iBenchStyle = 2 or iBenchStyle = 3 then _idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_frame_mat" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 1 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = "ui_list_surface_flat(1)" endif
if iBenchStyle = 1 or iBenchStyle = 4 then _idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_stand_mat" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 1 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = "ui_list_surface_flat(1)" endif
file_dependence "ui_list_contourPen_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_fillType_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_fillPen_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_fillBgPen_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_detailLevel3D_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_shadow_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_surface_flat(1)"
call "ui_object_Representation" parameters all listFieldID = TABID_RepresentationAndSurfaces, paramNameArray = paramNameReprArray, childFlagArray = childFlagReprArray, iconNameArray = iconNameReprArray
return
